## BatchLoader — ignore folder contents but keep the folders via .gitkeep
PiiRemover.BatchLoader/ocr-input/*
PiiRemover.BatchLoader/ocr-output/*
PiiRemover.BatchLoader/redact-input/*
PiiRemover.BatchLoader/redact-output/*
!PiiRemover.BatchLoader/ocr-input/.gitkeep
!PiiRemover.BatchLoader/ocr-output/.gitkeep
!PiiRemover.BatchLoader/redact-input/.gitkeep
!PiiRemover.BatchLoader/redact-output/.gitkeep

